{"markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"","page-layout":"full","format":{"html":{"theme":"cosmo","css":["styles.css"],"include-after-body":[{"text":"<script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/typed.js@2.0.12\"></script>\n<script defer src=\"assets/js/init-typed.js\"></script>\n<script defer src=\"assets/js/wavesurfer.min.js\"></script>\n<script defer src=\"assets/js/init-audio.js\"></script>\n"}]}}},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n<!-- ===== Varthai (edge-to-edge black) ===== -->\n<section class=\"page-columns page-full bg-black text-white\" aria-labelledby=\"hero-title\">\n  <div class=\"column-page p-0\">\n    <div class=\"min-vh-100 w-100 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center m-0\">\n      <h1 id=\"hero-title\" class=\"fw-bold text-center\">\n        <span id=\"typed-output\" aria-live=\"polite\">Varthai</span>\n      </h1>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ===== About (edge-to-edge grey with audio intro) ===== -->\n<section class=\"page-columns page-full bg-grey-f5\" aria-labelledby=\"about-title\">\n  <div class=\"column-page p-0\">\n    <div class=\"container py-5\">\n      <h2 id=\"about-title\" class=\"h1 mb-4\">About</h2>\n\n      <!-- Accessible fallback player (hidden once WaveSurfer mounts) -->\n      <audio id=\"about-audio\" src=\"assets/audio/intro.m4a\" preload=\"metadata\"></audio>\n\n      <div class=\"row g-4 align-items-center\">\n        <!-- Waveform + controls -->\n        <div class=\"col-lg-7\">\n          <div id=\"waveform\" class=\"rounded-3 shadow-sm\" aria-label=\"Audio waveform\"></div>\n\n          <div class=\"d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mt-3\">\n            <button id=\"btnPlay\" class=\"btn btn-dark px-4\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Play\">▶</button>\n            <div id=\"time\" class=\"text-muted small\" aria-live=\"polite\">0:00 / 0:00</div>\n            <div class=\"ms-auto small text-muted\">Intro to Varthai</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Transcript -->\n        <div class=\"col-lg-5\">\n          <div id=\"transcript\" class=\"transcript mt-4\">\n            <p data-start=\"0.00\" data-end=\"8.00\">\n              Hiya,<br>\n              Welcome to my homepage.<br>\n              My name is Vinayak.\n            </p>\n\n            <p data-start=\"8.00\" data-end=\"33.00\">\n              I am a methodologist, with a background in health behaviour change and an interest in making social science (particularly psychology and health psychology) more open.<br>\n              I’ve created this website to share my work and creative pursuits, and hopefully make them both accessible and engaging.\n            </p>\n\n            <p data-start=\"33.00\" data-end=\"54.00\">\n              I’m calling this project “Varthai”, which is a word from the Tamil language.<br>\n              It translates to “word” in English.<br>\n              The name comes from the idea that the same object can often be expressed using different words.\n            </p>\n\n            <p data-start=\"54.00\" data-end=\"76.00\">\n              So, in that vein, I’d like to use different words (in the metaphorical sense) to express my work.<br>\n              Through data visualisations, drawings and poetry, I’d like to have a word with you.\n            </p>\n\n            <p data-start=\"76.00\" data-end=\"90.00\">\n              Or to put it in Tamil:<br>\n              <strong>தரவு காட்சிப்படுத்தல்கள், ஓவியங்கள், கவிதைகள் மூலமா, உங்களோட ஒரு வார்த்தை பேச ஆசை.</strong>\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div> <!-- /.row -->\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ===== Reach out (edge-to-edge white) ===== -->\n<section class=\"page-columns page-full bg-white\">\n  <div class=\"column-page p-0\">\n    <div class=\"container py-5\">\n      <h2 class=\"h1 mb-4\">Reach out</h2>\n      <p class=\"text-muted mb-4\">You can find me or some of my work here:</p>\n      <div class=\"social-logos\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/vinayak-anand-kumar-de\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n          <img src=\"assets/img/icons/linkedin.svg\" alt=\"LinkedIn\">\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2972-5887\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n          <img src=\"assets/img/icons/orcid.svg\" alt=\"ORCID\">\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/Vinayak-NZ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n          <img src=\"assets/img/icons/github.svg\" alt=\"GitHub\">\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"https://osf.io/rg8s4/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n          <img src=\"assets/img/icons/osf.svg\" alt=\"OSF\">\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"https://zenodo.org/search?q=metadata.creators.person_or_org.name%3A%22Vinayak-NZ%22&l=list&p=1&s=10&sort=bestmatch\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n          <img src=\"assets/img/icons/zenodo.svg\" alt=\"Zenodo\">\n        </a>  \n        <a href=\"https://healthcascade.eu/about-us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n          <img src=\"assets/img/icons/hc.svg\" alt=\"healthcascade\">\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n```\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n<!-- ===== Varthai (edge-to-edge black) ===== -->\n<section class=\"page-columns page-full bg-black text-white\" aria-labelledby=\"hero-title\">\n  <div class=\"column-page p-0\">\n    <div class=\"min-vh-100 w-100 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center m-0\">\n      <h1 id=\"hero-title\" class=\"fw-bold text-center\">\n        <span id=\"typed-output\" aria-live=\"polite\">Varthai</span>\n      </h1>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ===== About (edge-to-edge grey with audio intro) ===== -->\n<section class=\"page-columns page-full bg-grey-f5\" aria-labelledby=\"about-title\">\n  <div class=\"column-page p-0\">\n    <div class=\"container py-5\">\n      <h2 id=\"about-title\" class=\"h1 mb-4\">About</h2>\n\n      <!-- Accessible fallback player (hidden once WaveSurfer mounts) -->\n      <aud